title: RE-Take CBR(Evangelion alternate ending doujin, complete RETake)
description:
In this torrent I upload proper CBR versions of the manga:
Neon Genesis Evangelion Re-take.

I got the files in a pdf format from another torrent here, however, and they were kinda disorganized and came in different picture sizes.

I reorganized them and combined them into 7 separate chapters.

Note:
There is some Hentai in there too but it's not the main lore, you may ignore it and skip to the relevant plot panels without losing track of the plot.

This story offers an alternative ending for the NGE anime, however, the NGE manga has an alternative ending too, you should try it as well:
 
https://thepiratebay.org/torrent/9360019/Neon_Genesis_Evangelion_Manga



Enjoy

May the fourth Rebuild movie of Evangelion will "unrape" my childhood.
